I am an Electronic Engineer by profession.

Currently I have knowledge and 3 years of experience in application development with React Native and Flutter. I like to test using Jest, to ensure the quality of my code

In my development career I use tools such as Git, Vscode, Command Line, Postman, Trello and Jira

I love to always learn the new and try to apply it to my work.
